{"id":1346,"date":"2024-08-04T20:46:12","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T20:46:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1346"},"modified":"2025-01-12T23:52:03","modified_gmt":"2025-01-12T23:52:03","slug":"mission-075","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-075\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #075: The Wayward Kid"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #075: The Wayward Kid<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Thundercap Mountain, 4F Maze Chamber &#8211; Milo the Pikachu-suited kid<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete the main story missions up until Great Desert<\/li>\n<li>Have the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf HM<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Help a lost Pikachu-suited kid to the exit in an area of 4F<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>TM73 Thunder Wave<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A kid is lost in the 4F Maze Chamber of Thundercap Mountain. Lead him to the exit successfully and he\u2019ll give you <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm073-thunder-wave\/\">TM73 Thunder Wave<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/01-pokemon-unbound-thundercap-mountain-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Thundercap Mountain entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Thundercap Mountain entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head to Thundercap Mountain, east of Epidimy Town.<\/p>\n<p>Go through the 1F cavern and climb the ladder up to 2F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-ladder-you-need.jpg\" alt=\"The ladder you need \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ladder you need<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you get to that level, head to a ladder in the middle of the cavern that leads up to a section of 3F that isn\u2019t the water-filled cave.<\/p>\n<p>Make sure you\u2019ve defeated Marlon at the summit of Thundercap, because if you haven\u2019t, a Shadow Grunt will be sleeping here, blocking your access.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-ladder-in-the-north.jpg\" alt=\"The ladder in the north \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ladder in the north<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once in the Tablet Chamber, go to the north ladder.  It will take you to a new area of 4F &#8211; the Maze Chamber.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/04-pokemon-unbound-1st-steps-in-the-maze-chamber.jpg\" alt=\"First steps in the Maze Chamber \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>First steps in the Maze Chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you arrive in the chamber, cross the pond to the east with Surf.<\/p>\n<p>Then, continue on east until you hit a corner area.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-corner-area.jpg\" alt=\"The corner area \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The corner area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From here, head north until you see an intersection.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-intersection.jpg\" alt=\"The intersection \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The intersection<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, head east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/07-pokemon-unbound-the-t-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The T-junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The T-junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll come to another T-junction. Go north and follow that tunnel around until you see a boy in a Pikachu outfit.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/08-pokemon-unbound-milo-needs-rescuing.jpg\" alt=\"Milo needs rescuing \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Milo needs rescuing<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>It\u2019s Milo, and he\u2019s stuck in this cave waiting for someone to lead him the way out.<\/p>\n<p>Agree, and he\u2019ll start following you. <\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> You will only be able to use your first three Pok\u00e9mon in battle, and he will battle alongside you in Double Battles with his two Pikachu. It\u2019s also worth noting you can\u2019t Surf while he is following you, so you can\u2019t simply go back across the pond.\n<\/div>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure><figcaption class=\"topcap\">(Click for full-size)<\/figcaption><figure class=\"img-modal\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/ImageObject\"><a itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/09-pokemon-unbound-the-most-efficient-path-to-the-exit-is-marked-by-the-red-line-fullsize.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" itemprop=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/09-pokemon-unbound-the-most-efficient-path-to-the-exit-is-marked-by-the-red-line.jpg\" alt=\"The most efficient path to the exit is marked by the red line \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><\/a><figcaption>The most efficient path to the exit is marked by the red line<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<p>Follow the map above to reach the ladder leading out of the cave.<\/p>\n<p>When Milo sees the ladder, that means your time escorting him is at an end and the mission is complete.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/075\/10-pokemon-unbound-milo-is-saved.jpg\" alt=\"Milo is saved \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Milo is saved<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>He\u2019ll thank you for your help with TM73 Thunder Wave.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1347,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1346","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1346","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1347"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1346"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1346"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}